Baby,
I am so sorry to leave you that emotional mess to listen to in the morning. I havenât had a break down like that in a VERY long time. Unfortunately, sometimes things get triggered.  

I donât want you to feel bad that you were not able to be there for me.  Because I made it thru on my own.  I opened up and let the emotions out and that is biggest part.  Letting out what was hurting me is the start to healing.  

I came home and took a long hot shower.  I made some sleepy tea and I am all nicely tucked into bed. I am wrapped in your blanket and listening to our playlist.  I am doing happy colour to make my eyes sleepy.

The part of all this that makes me feel the worst is the emotional turmoil I went through and left as messages for you.  I think the hardest part is to be that vulnerable and let you see me so broken.

If you are still reading thisâ¦
